
<h3>Contact Phil</h3>
<h6>Phil is available for local projects as well as potential employment opportunities. Use the form to inquire about rates and availability, or just to say 'Hi'. Phil can also be reached on 07967 085748</h6>

<div  class="container">
  <form action="sendfile" method="post">
